Tomorrow morning will be Vattoli's first mass!

545
00:46:36,240 --> 00:46:37,920
Let me see how smart he is!

546
00:46:38,680 --> 00:46:40,000
My god!

547
00:46:57,880 --> 00:46:59,560
No problem! You can wear it!

548
00:47:00,960 --> 00:47:03,360
Seems the church band lost this year also!

549
00:47:03,480 --> 00:47:05,280
- Yes, we lost Father! - What happened?

550
00:47:05,360 --> 00:47:07,200
That is a big story!

551
00:47:07,520 --> 00:47:10,840
Seems neighbouring parish got the trophy this time also!

552
00:47:10,880 --> 00:47:11,480
Right?

553
00:47:11,520 --> 00:47:14,120
