560
00:47:27,440 --> 00:47:29,240
That lady is flashy!

561
00:47:29,280 --> 00:47:31,680
She would wear a shirt, dhoti and a dark glass!

562
00:47:31,760 --> 00:47:32,440
Is it?

563
00:47:34,520 --> 00:47:35,960
Solomon, attend the call

564
00:47:36,000 --> 00:47:37,400
Father! I am scared to attend calls!

565
00:47:37,440 --> 00:47:38,800
There are just 2 phones in this town!

566
00:47:38,880 --> 00:47:41,560
One in contractor's house and another one in church!

567
00:47:44,720 --> 00:47:47,440
Your brother has assumed charge in a church!

568
00:47:47,520 --> 00:47:48,840
Can't you visit me?

569
00:47:48,880 --> 00:47:53,360
His aunt in Kayankulam slipped in bathroom!

570
00:47:53,480 --> 00:47:55,320
We had been there and just returned!

571
00:47:55,400 --> 00:47:57,080
Give it to me! Give

572
00:47:57,120 --> 00:47:58,920
The jack fruit stain will go on the phone!

573
00:47:58,960 --> 00:47:59,800
Dear Brother in law!

574
00:47:59,840 --> 00:48:01,000
Big brother in law!

575
00:48:01,200 --> 00:48:02,560
Dear brother in law!

576
00:48:02,640 --> 00:48:04,080
Big brother in law!

577
00:48:04,760 --> 00:48:07,280
What is the news! Did you not go home?

578
00:48:07,320 --> 00:48:09,760
I had to come here earlier for some wok

579
00:48:09,840 --> 00:48:12,000
Any way, if you call from the other banks...

580
00:48:12,040 --> 00:48:14,440
...me and your sister would reach there!

581
00:48:14,480 --> 00:48:16,520
Did you meet Ottapla Father?

582
00:48:16,800 --> 00:48:20,360
Yes I met him, taunted and then only came here!

583
00:48:20,920 --> 00:48:25,320
Your younger brother is taunting Ottapla Father!

584
00:48:26,160 --> 00:48:29,080
Have you started your pranks!

585
00:48:30,000 --> 00:48:32,840
If I come to know any of your mischieves there...

586
00:48:32,920 --> 00:48:34,680
I would immediately come there in a boat!

587
00:48:34,760 --> 00:48:35,760
Ok

588
00:48:37,920 --> 00:48:39,080
Is it your sister, Father?

589
00:48:39,720 --> 00:48:42,440
We have only one sister, Mariamma!

590
00:48:43,400 --> 00:48:44,800
- You know her - Is it?

591
00:48:44,920 --> 00:48:48,200
She is married to Thommeri Davis of the other bank!

592
00:48:50,880 --> 00:48:53,040
I take leave Father! It is time to ring the bell!

593
00:48:53,080 --> 00:48:54,360
Solomon, wait!

594
00:48:55,320 --> 00:48:57,040
You complained about my sister and brother in law

595
00:48:57,120 --> 00:48:58,680
How can you leave just like that!

596
00:48:58,720 --> 00:49:00,200
I don't know anything

597
00:49:00,560 --> 00:49:02,600
Vincent Vattoli from Changanaserry...

598
00:49:02,640 --> 00:49:05,760
Why should he choose Kumarangiri parish to become a junior vicar?

599
00:49:05,800 --> 00:49:06,840
Do you know Solomon?

600
00:49:07,440 --> 00:49:08,400
I don't know Father!

601
00:49:08,440 --> 00:49:11,480
Will the church band survive tomorrow's voting?

602
00:49:11,560 --> 00:49:13,520
What do you think Solomon?

603
00:49:13,880 --> 00:49:15,440
I don't know about that too, Father!

604
00:49:15,640 --> 00:49:17,280
But I have understood one thing!

605
00:49:17,560 --> 00:49:19,280
It is a concerted planned move!

606
00:49:21,560 --> 00:49:23,720
Gee Varghese band does not belong to the church alone!

607
00:49:23,760 --> 00:49:26,720
It belongs to this town and also to the Lord in this church!

608
00:49:27,280 --> 00:49:29,400
I don't want anything to happen to the band!

609
00:49:44,720 --> 00:49:50,600
Before we decide to continue or not the Saint Gee Varghese band...

610
00:49:50,640 --> 00:49:54,440
...our church's new priest Father Vincent Vattoli

611
00:49:54,520 --> 00:49:57,600
...would address you briefly!

612
00:50:11,600 --> 00:50:14,960
I saw this place for the first time on a new year day long ago!

613
00:50:15,160 --> 00:50:16,560
I was a young child then!

614
00:50:17,440 --> 00:50:19,680
I was like the little son sitting in front!

615
00:50:19,760 --> 00:50:21,880
- What is your name son? - Joy mon!

616
00:50:22,640 --> 00:50:23,760
I was like Joy mon!

617
00:50:25,160 --> 00:50:27,760
That day my dad said something to his brother!

618
00:50:27,840 --> 00:50:29,280
That is still ringing in my ears!

619
00:50:29,360 --> 00:50:31,160
In Kumarangiri, one can't find a person...

620
00:50:31,200 --> 00:50:35,000
...who has not hummed a song or who has not fallen in love at least once

621
00:50:35,080 --> 00:50:36,680
When I stepped in to this place...

622
00:50:36,720 --> 00:50:40,280
...my dad and uncle took me first to this church!

623
00:50:40,640 --> 00:50:43,560
Through the big gathering...

624
00:50:43,640 --> 00:50:47,600
...what struck me first was a priceless thing!

625
00:50:48,080 --> 00:50:51,800
People who came out of the church touched and caressed that!

626
00:50:51,880 --> 00:50:53,320
It is still vivid in my memory!

627
00:50:53,920 --> 00:50:56,800
After many years I have returned to this place as a priest!

628
00:50:56,960 --> 00:50:59,880
When I entered the Saint's church again...

629
00:50:59,920 --> 00:51:05,080
...my eyes were looking for that invaluable thing!

630
00:51:19,640 --> 00:51:22,000
It is there It is still here!

631
00:52:00,840 --> 00:52:03,960
When I returned on that day in boat with dad and uncle...

632
00:52:04,000 --> 00:52:07,800
...along with ice stick and toys I took along one more thing

633
00:52:08,320 --> 00:52:09,920
The music of this town!

634
00:52:10,400 --> 00:52:13,960
The music of this place made Kumarangiri renowned!

635
00:52:14,360 --> 00:52:17,440
That music was shared to everyone who lived here...

636
00:52:17,800 --> 00:52:19,600
...by the saint Gee Varghese band!

637
00:52:20,080 --> 00:52:22,720
That band is now like this neglected piano...

638
00:52:22,920 --> 00:52:28,480
...full of dust and is getting ready to receive its last rites!

639
00:52:29,320 --> 00:52:34,200
Esthappan master, Itteri, Kochu Thommy, Antappan

640
00:52:34,880 --> 00:52:38,240
What was drowned in the lake was merely their bodies!

641
00:52:39,240 --> 00:52:43,000
You have forgotten all of them After having lost all near and dear...

642
00:52:43,040 --> 00:52:45,040
...Pope Louis is, still living for the sake of music!

643
00:52:45,120 --> 00:52:46,920
If you don't want him...

644
00:52:46,960 --> 00:52:50,240
...you would be losing the soul of Kumarangiri

645
00:52:50,600 --> 00:52:52,280
...and also Kumarangiri's music

646
00:52:53,200 --> 00:52:58,000
Let that music bring back excitement and integration of this town

647
00:52:59,000 --> 00:53:01,200
Should we not submit the ever rolling trophy...

648
00:53:01,240 --> 00:53:02,960
...at the feet of the saint again?

649
00:53:03,600 --> 00:53:05,320
What do you say Lonappan brother?

650
00:53:06,480 --> 00:53:07,880
Don't you want Ittoop brother?

651
00:53:13,520 --> 00:53:15,680
- What about you Joy mon? - I want

652
00:53:16,640 --> 00:53:18,920
Should we dissolve the church band?

653
00:53:19,000 --> 00:53:22,440
No No

654
00:53:23,720 --> 00:53:24,960
No

655
00:53:51,200 --> 00:53:54,640
Father! You could have contested the election!

656
00:53:54,960 --> 00:53:57,080
I have contested and won too!

657
00:54:02,320 --> 00:54:05,480
"The entire village looked in overwhelming surprise!"

658
00:54:06,200 --> 00:54:08,400
"From where did this divine messenger come?"

659
00:54:08,520 --> 00:54:11,960
"You caress while weaving a tender leaf garland!"

660
00:54:12,000 --> 00:54:16,240
"You have changed the feeble wind! Is it a fortune for this town?"

661
00:54:16,280 --> 00:54:20,080
"Your flair is throbbing and shining outwardly!"

662
00:54:20,120 --> 00:54:21,800
"Welcome you Welcome you!"

663
00:54:21,920 --> 00:54:23,640
"You are a pulsating fortitude!"

664
00:54:23,680 --> 00:54:25,400
"Vattoli father's gait is graceful and rhythmic"

665
00:54:25,440 --> 00:54:27,320
"It's a rhythmic sway to left and right!"

666
00:54:27,400 --> 00:54:31,280
"Have you not noticed his captivating smile!"

667
00:54:31,400 --> 00:54:35,000
"How elegant he is! It is a treat to watch!"

668
00:54:35,080 --> 00:54:37,560
"We are endowed with this gift today!"

669
00:54:37,720 --> 00:54:38,960
"Vattoli!"

670
00:54:39,120 --> 00:54:42,600
"His words are coated with honey! His looks are serene!"

671
00:54:42,640 --> 00:54:44,720
"You are a fortune to this town!"

672
00:54:44,800 --> 00:54:46,800
"Vattoli"

673
00:54:53,720 --> 00:54:57,160
"The gentle breeze from south is nippy!"

674
00:54:57,200 --> 00:55:02,200
"To get over the chill you fell in campfire and wine!"

675
00:55:09,080 --> 00:55:11,080
"The gentle breeze from south is nippy!"

676
00:55:11,120 --> 00:55:17,280
"To get over the chill you fell in campfire and wine!"

677
00:55:17,320 --> 00:55:19,160
"Sunshine of Kumaram!"

678
00:55:19,200 --> 00:55:21,080
"Good people vowed for betterment..."

679
00:55:21,120 --> 00:55:25,200
"...you sprouted like a golden ray from a mango seed!"

680
00:55:25,280 --> 00:55:28,760
"You are like Kuravilangadu saviour! Country's first sailor captain!"

681
00:55:28,800 --> 00:55:32,760
"It is cherubic! The song and rhythm!"

682
00:55:32,840 --> 00:55:36,480
"Like an harvest let us celebrate!"

683
00:55:39,160 --> 00:55:41,000
"Vattoli!"

684
00:55:46,320 --> 00:55:48,160
"Vattoli!"

685
00:55:51,120 --> 00:55:52,560
"Vattoli!"

686
00:56:11,280 --> 00:56:13,160
"Vattoli!"

687
00:56:13,720 --> 00:56:15,800
He is wearing pants and sun glasses!

688
00:56:15,880 --> 00:56:17,280
Is he a Father?

689
00:56:20,440 --> 00:56:22,240
Saint has sent us Vattoli Father!

690
00:56:22,320 --> 00:56:24,440
- Sufficient for one load - My god!

691
00:57:10,920 --> 00:57:14,000
Say so You are an artist!

692
00:57:14,160 --> 00:57:19,120
Yesterday I thought why should a Father coming from eastern hill side...

693
00:57:19,160 --> 00:57:22,160
...argue for Gee Varghese band?

694
00:57:22,240 --> 00:57:24,600
That is why I said only those who drink toddy...

695
00:57:24,640 --> 00:57:27,200
...will know the taste of the carp fish!

696
00:57:28,080 --> 00:57:29,200
Is it not?

697
00:57:30,080 --> 00:57:31,200
Come in!

698
00:57:33,080 --> 00:57:34,440
Have you seen her Father?

699
00:57:34,560 --> 00:57:36,600
She is from France Michelle

700
00:57:36,800 --> 00:57:38,480
All those who came with her have returned!

701
00:57:38,520 --> 00:57:41,160
She wants to learn our music and stayed back!

702
00:57:41,240 --> 00:57:43,720
Her parents are not in agreement with her

703
00:57:43,800 --> 00:57:44,920
She is a smart girl!

704
00:57:45,640 --> 00:57:47,720
Child! This is Father Vincent!

705
00:57:47,840 --> 00:57:49,920
He is our church's new junior vicar!

706
00:57:52,880 --> 00:57:55,480
Pappan! Shouldn't Solomon practice playing!

707
00:57:55,680 --> 00:57:59,160
Let him first learn to hold it properly Father!

708
00:57:59,840 --> 00:58:01,080
Is it not Charlie?

709
00:58:03,920 --> 00:58:06,360
When one plays it should not be merely blowing out air!

710
00:58:06,440 --> 00:58:08,240
Music should also come!

711
00:58:23,520 --> 00:58:26,360
You are a Father in the Church!

712
00:58:27,080 --> 00:58:27,920
Yes

713
00:58:30,360 --> 00:58:33,280
But the other day you danced with me in the boat!

714
00:58:34,920 --> 00:58:36,640
I understand English!

715
00:58:36,720 --> 00:58:39,560
But I like to talk in Malayalam!

716
00:58:39,880 --> 00:58:42,720
I can understand Malayalam!

717
00:58:42,960 --> 00:58:46,040
What is wrong in both of us dancing together?

718
00:58:46,520 --> 00:58:50,320
People and your culture...

719
00:58:50,440 --> 00:58:52,960
...would miscon-

720
00:58:53,160 --> 00:58:54,800
Will not misconstrue

721
00:58:56,400 --> 00:58:59,040
People with good intentions never misconstrue!

722
00:58:59,200 --> 00:59:01,360
They will look at us as two human beings!

723
01:00:08,360 --> 01:00:10,280
It is like a cinema scene!

724
01:00:10,400 --> 01:00:12,360
You dog! Go

725
01:00:29,880 --> 01:00:31,360
Stop there!

726
01:00:34,160 --> 01:00:38,440
You need not bathe at home sacristan!

727
01:00:41,520 --> 01:00:43,040
I did not insist on selling the house...

728
01:00:43,080 --> 01:00:44,880
...because I don't want you and kids to be left in lurch!

729
01:00:44,920 --> 01:00:45,960
I have made some computations

730
01:00:46,000 --> 01:00:47,760
I will take a decision shortly about that!

731
01:00:47,800 --> 01:00:49,640
Then you decide quickly and inform us

732
01:00:49,720 --> 01:00:51,240
Should we also not know about it?

733
01:00:51,280 --> 01:00:53,240
- You... - Don't do it dad!

734
01:00:53,320 --> 01:00:54,080
Hope you know...

735
01:00:54,160 --> 01:00:56,800
If I consider the interest and compound interest Esthappan owe...

736
01:00:56,840 --> 01:00:59,480
...even if the house is sold you may have to pay me

737
01:00:59,560 --> 01:01:01,000
Went there to help them!

738
01:01:01,040 --> 01:01:04,680
Come fast! I left the dinner half way

739
01:01:05,000 --> 01:01:07,080
'The food left over by sacristan...'

740
01:01:07,240 --> 01:01:13,240
'...would have been by now consumed by his pet dog Chakki!'

741
01:01:13,680 --> 01:01:15,720
'The deal for Chakki will follow'

742
01:01:30,800 --> 01:01:31,920
Stay there!

743
01:01:35,520 --> 01:01:42,400
'That night 7 1/2 year old chakki died due to sacristan's fatal blows!'

744
01:01:49,880 --> 01:01:51,720
Is there anything tastier than this?

745
01:01:51,840 --> 01:01:53,760
Couldn't you get some fish?

746
01:01:55,600 --> 01:01:57,960
Is anything stuffed in your throat?

747
01:01:58,080 --> 01:02:00,880
No point in opening your mouth when you come for food!

748
01:02:01,240 --> 01:02:03,280
Do you know what is happening here?

749
01:02:03,320 --> 01:02:04,200
How will you know?

750
01:02:04,280 --> 01:02:06,240
All the time you roam around carrying the clarinet!

751
01:02:06,320 --> 01:02:08,320
My dad's name is Esthappan!

752
01:02:08,360 --> 01:02:09,760
I will roam with the clarinet!

753
01:02:09,840 --> 01:02:12,360
I care a damn if others feel bad about it!

754
01:02:12,400 --> 01:02:14,840
For one week I have been telling you to change the bulb!

755
01:02:14,880 --> 01:02:16,800
Today mom went there and fell down

756
01:02:16,840 --> 01:02:20,680
Until now she was screaming! She has just gone to bed!

757
01:02:32,720 --> 01:02:36,080
When can I see you thriving?

758
01:02:37,000 --> 01:02:40,920
I will die only after seeing you well off

759
01:02:44,400 --> 01:02:46,400
I don't know mom!

760
01:02:54,480 --> 01:02:55,760
Don't cry dear

761
01:03:03,240 --> 01:03:04,000
Clara!

762
01:03:04,760 --> 01:03:07,080
- Is Solomon not there? - He is inside!

763
01:03:07,200 --> 01:03:07,880
What is it?

764
01:03:07,920 --> 01:03:09,360
He has been asked to go to the church!

765
01:03:09,440 --> 01:03:11,080
Junior Vicar has a session!

766
01:03:11,160 --> 01:03:12,280
Is it?

767
01:03:13,160 --> 01:03:14,040
Yes, bro

768
01:03:14,120 --> 01:03:15,600
I have just come from church!

769
01:03:15,680 --> 01:03:17,640
You may leave! I will go

770
01:03:27,040 --> 01:03:28,760
Give me some water, Clara!

771
01:03:29,120 --> 01:03:30,040
No

772
01:03:30,280 --> 01:03:31,880
I asked because of thirst!

773
01:03:59,360 --> 01:04:00,800
Does this hen lay eggs?

774
01:04:01,000 --> 01:04:04,480
No, it lays orange Shall I get some?

775
01:04:06,480 --> 01:04:09,200
Give that vessel I have other works to do

776
01:04:10,400 --> 01:04:12,360
Wait for a moment!

777
01:04:12,880 --> 01:04:15,200
I saw you keeping the paper there!

778
01:04:15,280 --> 01:04:16,920
Seems you took great troubles!

779
01:04:17,000 --> 01:04:20,800
If you drink water like this you will find time only to urinate!

780
01:04:20,840 --> 01:04:22,200
Have you not gone yet?

781
01:04:22,240 --> 01:04:23,160
Get into the boat! I am coming!

782
01:04:23,240 --> 01:04:24,480
Has Nancy come for delivery?

783
01:04:24,520 --> 01:04:25,440
Yes

784
