1560
02:02:13,600 --> 02:02:16,080
- Is this a new one? - No, it is an old one Father!

1561
02:02:16,400 --> 02:02:18,840
So, tomorrow will you play with this?

1562
02:02:22,160 --> 02:02:24,200
So the church band will win, right?

1563
02:02:25,120 --> 02:02:28,720
For your sake you want me to lose!

1564
02:02:42,520 --> 02:02:47,600
Now play tomorrow and try to win!

1565
02:03:05,000 --> 02:03:07,360
My God! What is it?

1566
02:03:08,520 --> 02:03:11,320
Son! What happened?

1567
02:03:13,000 --> 02:03:16,080
Jesus! Tell me son!

1568
02:03:16,360 --> 02:03:18,040
How will I play tomorrow!

1569
02:03:19,360 --> 02:03:20,640
My clarinet...

1570
02:03:23,080 --> 02:03:25,240
To play, I...

1571
02:03:55,080 --> 02:03:56,280
Is this not dad's?

1572
02:03:56,360 --> 02:03:58,240
I don't want to learn what happened!

1573
02:03:58,480 --> 02:04:00,840
Tomorrow you are playing with this!

1574
02:04:08,040 --> 02:04:12,680
It is our dad's desire that you should play with this at stage tomorrow!

1575
02:04:14,160 --> 02:04:21,360
I didn't know my brother is a whizz than our dad!

1576
02:04:21,720 --> 02:04:23,040
I didn't know about it!

1577
02:05:36,160 --> 02:05:40,640
Shoshanna! Don't ask me where is the clarinet you gave me?

1578
02:05:41,240 --> 02:05:42,680
That is no more with me

1579
02:05:43,640 --> 02:05:45,040
This is my dad's

1580
02:05:45,800 --> 02:05:47,160
Esthappan master's!

1581
02:05:48,040 --> 02:05:51,440
Wherever he has taken this or used he has seen only victories!

1582
02:05:52,360 --> 02:05:54,320
But I am not Esthappan master!

1583
02:05:55,760 --> 02:05:57,800
Have I ever won?

1584
02:05:59,440 --> 02:06:03,320
If I take the stage tomorrow, our band will lose!

1585
02:06:04,360 --> 02:06:05,640
I am going!

1586
02:06:06,160 --> 02:06:07,480
I can't...

1587
02:06:07,760 --> 02:06:10,560
Will you go? Will you lose?

1588
02:06:11,640 --> 02:06:15,960
If you lose, along with you Louis Pappan who has faith in you will also lose

1589
02:06:17,080 --> 02:06:18,680
Kumarangiri will also lose!

1590
02:06:20,760 --> 02:06:22,240
Don't you want to win?

1591
02:06:24,160 --> 02:06:25,840
Don't you want to marry me?

1592
02:07:05,840 --> 02:07:09,120
Whose screams you were responding at this midnight?

1593
02:07:09,280 --> 02:07:10,280
I will go!

1594
02:07:10,520 --> 02:07:13,360
If my Solomon calls I will go even if it is midnight!

1595
02:07:28,920 --> 02:07:31,440
Tomorrow will be your guys last day playing of the instrument!

1596
02:07:31,480 --> 02:07:34,880
Let me see how you will reach the church premises!

1597
02:07:35,520 --> 02:07:37,640
Until we return from the church tomorrow...

1598
02:07:37,680 --> 02:07:38,880
...don't open the door!

1599
02:07:40,480 --> 02:07:43,360
Aunt! Ask him to open the door!

1600
02:07:43,880 --> 02:07:46,280
Brother! Open it!

1601
02:07:52,600 --> 02:07:55,600
Vattoli! Are you going to hit me?

1602
02:08:00,560 --> 02:08:04,840
I don't want others to know about certain things!

1603
02:08:05,200 --> 02:08:06,640
Tell me, what it is!

1604
02:08:11,120 --> 02:08:13,280
What you did yesterday were deeds not supposed...

1605
02:08:13,360 --> 02:08:14,960
...to be done by a person wearing the robe!

1606
02:08:15,000 --> 02:08:15,960
What is it?

1607
02:08:16,240 --> 02:08:18,120
You broke Solomon's clarinet...

1608
02:08:18,200 --> 02:08:21,280
...you don't even qualify to be a human being, Father!

1609
02:08:22,000 --> 02:08:25,440
I am wearing this robe for the last 40 years!

1610
02:08:25,840 --> 02:08:30,800
You need not teach me the do's and don'ts of wearing this robe!

1611
02:08:32,800 --> 02:08:36,680
Diocese has not given you robe and authority to help a girl whose engagement...

1612
02:08:36,760 --> 02:08:39,680
...is over to elope with someone!

1613
02:08:41,040 --> 02:08:43,760
One does not become a father to work against...

1614
02:08:43,840 --> 02:08:49,560
...the church, diocese, superiors and noble Christians

1615
02:08:51,240 --> 02:08:54,920
Bible says a tree that does not produce fruit...

1616
02:08:55,000 --> 02:08:57,280
...will be cut down and thrown into the fire

1617
02:08:58,000 --> 02:09:03,320
But what I learned evidently from bible is 'let us love one another'

1618
02:09:04,080 --> 02:09:09,240
Father, you have time only to roam around with a foreign woman!

1619
02:09:11,840 --> 02:09:15,880
Locals say you would soon discard the robes!

1620
02:09:15,960 --> 02:09:20,720
Those days locals said the same thing about Jesus and Mary Magdalene

1621
02:09:21,520 --> 02:09:24,720
It was Lord Jesus Christ who was crucified

1622
02:09:24,800 --> 02:09:26,560
Not Father Vincent Vattoli!

1623
02:09:27,520 --> 02:09:31,320
So let us not try to taunt each other on this score!

1624
02:09:31,880 --> 02:09:34,880
You believe, if you close your eyes, it is night!

1625
02:09:35,280 --> 02:09:39,640
Don't think no one knows the motive behind the church demolition!

1626
02:09:40,680 --> 02:09:44,760
For certain deeds I follow my own style!

1627
02:09:45,640 --> 02:09:50,360
I will do what is required to make others also think in those lines!

1628
02:09:50,520 --> 02:09:52,880
You are not the congregation!

1629
02:09:53,200 --> 02:09:56,560
But I am the vicar of the Kumarangiri church!

1630
02:09:56,960 --> 02:10:01,080
Whether it is demolition of church or dissolving the band...

1631
02:10:01,120 --> 02:10:06,640
...or Shoshanna's marriage with Solomon it is I who take the final decision!

1632
02:10:08,240 --> 02:10:14,320
On top of that is the saint who protects the church and Lord Jesus!

1633
02:10:14,640 --> 02:10:16,960
They will also have made some decisions!

1634
02:10:19,080 --> 02:10:20,960
Father! Have a cup of coffee!

1635
02:10:21,520 --> 02:10:23,160
The competition is about to start!

1636
02:10:29,160 --> 02:10:30,080
No thanks, Father!

1637
02:10:30,320 --> 02:10:32,480
Will have coffee after the competition!

1638
02:10:34,160 --> 02:10:37,840
I...I will stay here!

1639
02:10:38,400 --> 02:10:44,520
Me and the saint want to hear you play and win!

1640
02:10:45,200 --> 02:10:46,320
Chali!

1641
02:11:05,920 --> 02:11:09,640
Dear friends! The exciting contest is about to start!

1642
02:11:09,720 --> 02:11:14,520
The two teams are ready like war horses!

1643
02:11:14,560 --> 02:11:17,240
I read your letter kept inside the rafter!

1644
02:11:18,520 --> 02:11:21,360
Try to play well and win! I will give you a reply then!

1645
02:11:25,320 --> 02:11:30,760
Clap your hands and encourage them! Yes clap like that!

1646
02:11:33,200 --> 02:11:35,760
Competition is going to start!

1647
02:11:35,840 --> 02:11:42,360
Dear friends! We welcome you all to witness this competition!

1648
02:11:47,240 --> 02:11:51,960
Dear friends! The exciting contest is about to start!

1649
02:11:52,040 --> 02:11:56,120
We invite both teams to the stage!

1650
02:12:11,560 --> 02:12:15,360
Both teams have occupied the dais!

1651
02:12:15,440 --> 02:12:19,480
Both teams are charged up electrifying competition!

1652
02:12:19,520 --> 02:12:24,080
Few minutes from now the competition starts!

1653
02:12:24,160 --> 02:12:26,840
Come on clap! Come on

1654
02:12:27,600 --> 02:12:32,560
Play soft where required and loud where required!

1655
02:12:32,640 --> 02:12:38,720
The clarinet now in your hand will decide whether you should live or not!

1656
02:12:39,280 --> 02:12:43,000
A sobbing person with prayers is sitting inside!

1657
02:12:43,080 --> 02:12:44,320
Don't forget that!

1658
02:12:46,200 --> 02:12:50,440
Did you not hear how he played the third tempo yesterday!

1659
02:12:50,720 --> 02:12:54,720
Is he the guy who is going to defeat me and win the trophy?

1660
02:12:55,960 --> 02:12:58,680
Today he would poop while playing!

1661
02:14:31,840 --> 02:14:37,760
"It is a prayer to Saint Gee Varghese"

1662
02:16:27,880 --> 02:16:29,600
"Challenge or defiance!"

1663
02:16:29,680 --> 02:16:31,720
"Even if we die we would not give up!"

1664
02:16:31,800 --> 02:16:33,400
"Challenge or defiance!"

1665
02:16:33,480 --> 02:16:35,560
"Even if we die we would not give up!"

1666
02:16:35,640 --> 02:16:39,440
"Defeat stares you! But putting up a brave face!"

1667
02:16:39,520 --> 02:16:43,160
"Defeat stares you! But putting up a brave face!"

1668
02:16:43,240 --> 02:16:49,560
"Challenge or defiance!"

1669
02:16:50,840 --> 02:16:56,880
"Death or defeat...!"

1670
02:20:58,960 --> 02:21:02,920
I don't know about the decision of the judges!

1671
02:21:03,040 --> 02:21:05,280
But I know about one thing!

1672
02:21:05,840 --> 02:21:10,960
I can't play better than this!

1673
02:22:50,720 --> 02:22:53,600
'Perhaps he did not want to witness the church demolition!'

1674
02:22:53,760 --> 02:22:56,280
'So he left us earlier!'

1675
02:23:16,240 --> 02:23:18,200
- Philipose! - What is it, Father?

1676
02:23:20,040 --> 02:23:21,280
Solomon! You proceed!

1677
02:23:23,200 --> 02:23:26,240
Should we not take a decision on this?

1678
02:23:26,280 --> 02:23:27,160
About what?

1679
02:23:27,800 --> 02:23:29,720
You made a promise!

1680
02:23:29,800 --> 02:23:31,760
If Solomon wins the competition...

1681
02:23:31,840 --> 02:23:34,520
You mean that one...!

1682
02:23:35,480 --> 02:23:40,240
Me making a promise on street and he winning the trophy is all true

1683
02:23:40,320 --> 02:23:42,200
But how can I give my daughter to him?

1684
02:23:42,280 --> 02:23:44,440
Is this a child's play, Father?

1685
02:23:45,600 --> 02:23:47,240
I can consider about it...

1686
02:23:47,320 --> 02:23:53,000
...if the guy who played the bet with me who is in grave or the saint tells me

1687
02:23:53,800 --> 02:24:00,080
As I decided earlier, my daughter would marry Davis's nephew

1688
02:24:00,160 --> 02:24:01,320
Is it not Davis?

1689
02:24:01,400 --> 02:24:04,880
If that is to happen my dad should not be Thommeri Kochu Pappan

1690
02:24:04,960 --> 02:24:07,160
If you are manly honor your words!

1691
02:24:07,240 --> 02:24:10,360
For idiotic acts like this don't expect my support!

1692
02:24:11,960 --> 02:24:16,160
After the first mass and first consecration of the new church...

1693
02:24:16,200 --> 02:24:19,320
...the first wedding at the new church will be my daughter's

1694
02:24:19,400 --> 02:24:24,520
We will invite all and sundry! Come and enjoy the free feast!

1695
02:24:25,400 --> 02:24:26,280
Go guys!

1696
02:24:27,400 --> 02:24:28,360
Come Matha!

1697
02:24:29,280 --> 02:24:30,200
Move away!

1698
02:24:58,920 --> 02:25:00,680
First remove the saint!

1699
02:25:00,760 --> 02:25:02,320
Then do the rest!

1700
02:25:39,440 --> 02:25:43,760
'Kumarangiri rained for one full day and night!'

1701
02:25:43,840 --> 02:25:46,920
'Along with that 3 great things happened!'

1702
02:25:47,440 --> 02:25:53,080
'Father Ottplakan had a dream that the church need not be demolished'

1703
02:25:53,160 --> 02:25:57,680
'Contractor Philipose understood Shoshanna is destined to be Solomon's wife!'

1704
02:25:58,040 --> 02:26:03,800
